com.btilm305.clashapi

Interface ClanData

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AbbreviatedClan, Clan

    public interface ClanData
    The simplest representation of a Clan, containing only a few data fields. All API calls that return clan data contain at least this amount of information.

    More information about a clan can be requested with ClashAPI.requestClan(ClanData)
